Package net.canarymod.commandsys.commands.playermod

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PlayerCreate
    Command to add a player (for permissions, groups, etc.) to the database
    PlayerGroupAdd
    Command to add a group to a player
    PlayerGroupCheck
    Command to check if a player is in a group
    PlayerGroupList
    Command to list all the groups a player belongs to
    PlayerGroupRemove
    Command to remove a group from a player (not main group)
    PlayerGroupSet
    Command to set a players group
    PlayermodBase
    Command to show help for the playermod command
    PlayerPermissionAdd
    Command to add a permission node to a player
    PlayerPermissionCheck
    Command to check if a player has a permission node
    PlayerPermissionList
    Command to list all permissions a player has
    PlayerPermissionRemove
    Command to remove a permission node from a player
    PlayerPrefix
    Command to change the prefix of a player
    PlayerRemove
    Command to remove player data from the database
